data.description:
Welcome to your dream home on 29 acres with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an additional office space.  The expansive 29 acres provide ample space for outdoor activities, whether you're interested in gardening, starting your own farm, or simply enjoying the peaceful views. the property comes with a detached 2 car garage with a workshop in the back, a 2-stall barn, an additional 3-stall barn, a hay barn and a large walk-in doghouse. Fully fenced with separated pens for multiple horses or other livestock. 
Full electric home but has propane available with an owned tank that stays with the property. 
HVAC and water heater just over a year old. 
Additional septic tank, water and electric available on the property in case you wanted to add another home. 
18 miles to the new American Heartland Theme Park.
